     <header class="article-header"> 
      <h1 class="article-title"><a href="http://www.99xiuxiu.com/1839.html">如何通过公众号做一场完美的国庆推广活动？</a></h1> 
      <div class="meta"> 
       <span id="mute-category" class="muted"><i class="fa fa-list-alt"></i><a href="http://www.99xiuxiu.com/yunying"> 运营与推广</a></span> 
       <span class="muted"><i class="fa fa-user"></i> <a href="http://www.99xiuxiu.com/author/wangshitou">王石头</a></span> 
       <time class="muted"><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> 6个月前 (09-28)</time> 
       <span class="muted"><i class="fa fa-eye"></i> 553次浏览</span> 
       <span class="muted"><i class="fa fa-flag"></i> <a target="_blank" title="点击查看" rel="external nofollow" href="http://www.baidu.com/s?wd=如何通过公众号做一场完美的国庆推广活动？">已收录</a></span> 
       <span class="muted"><i class="fa fa-comments-o"></i> <a href="http://www.99xiuxiu.com/1839.html#respond">0个评论</a></span> 
       <span class="muted"></span> 
      </div> 
     </header> 
     <div class="banner banner-post">
      <!-- 广告位：PC ##正文标题下## --> 
      <script>
